text: chea karpit nasa yeung ban banhchoun nuo h towkean krom robsa ke haey ke ban pol tha ao krom robsakhnhom. chaur puok anak korp sakkar champoh a l laoh choh puok anak kmean mcheasa na phe sa ng pi trong laey . pitabrakd nasa khnhom pruoybaromph khlach puok anak ttuol tearounakamm nea thngai da mhema( thngai barlok)
